{"type": "article", "id": 29519, "title": "ASOS 预计全年销售额大涨，以及，多品牌发布秋冬大片｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-13T02:39:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8, "name": "奢侈品"}, {"id": 9, "name": "意大利"}, {"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 6132, "name": "加拿大"}, {"id": 10455, "name": "店铺"}, {"id": 10705, "name": "大理石"}, {"id": 15794, "name": "秋冬"}, {"id": 1330, "name": "ASOS"}, {"id": 1425, "name": "Saint Laurent"}, {"id": 7502, "name": "Farfetch"}, {"id": 8084, "name": "Marni"}, {"id": 18474, "name": "Free people"}, {"id": 28261, "name": "BFC"}, {"id": 30126, "name": "Armani Exchange"}, {"id": 30128, "name": "Lancôme"}, {"id": 30129, "name": "Taylor Hill"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160713103249oFACB4vX0bE3Ik7i.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/british-fashion-council-names-three-non-executive-directors-10485168/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国时装协会任命三位非执行董事</b></a>｜英国时装协会（BFC）近日宣布英国 <i>GQ</i> 主编 Dylan Jones、奢侈品电商 Farfetch 创始人兼 CEO José Neves、卫报传媒集团（GMG） CEO David Pemsel 将担任 BFC 非执行董事，加入董事会。此前董事会成员包括主席  Natalie Massenet、CEO Caroline Rush、非执行董事 Anya Hindmarch。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/taylor-hill-named-lancome-ambassador-10486312/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Taylor Hill 担任兰蔻大使</b></a>｜欧莱雅旗下品牌兰蔻（Lancôme）近日宣布，美国模特 Taylor Hill 担任品牌形象大使，2017 年 1 月将上线她为兰蔻拍摄的彩妆及护肤品牌广告。Taylor 是新晋的维密天使，为很多主要时尚品牌走秀及拍摄广告。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Asos-sees-full-year-sales-growth-at-upper-end-of-guidance,712786.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>ASOS 预计全年销售额有大幅上涨</b></a>｜英国时装电商 ASOS 近日宣布调高全年销售额预期，在截至 6 月 30 日的前四个月内，总销售额上涨了 30% 至 5.005 亿英镑（约合 6.541 亿美元），超出分析师 22.9% 的预期。英国境内销售额上涨 28%，国际销售额则增长了 31%。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/7/12/12159322/colourpop-international-shipping\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Colourpop 开启全球递送</b></a>｜南加州创立仅仅两年的独立彩妆品牌 Colourpop，在 YouTube 和 Instagram （<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/colourpopcosmetics/\" rel=\"nofollow\">主页有 280 万粉丝</a>）上都很火，今日宣布开启全球递送服务，主打的 6 美元唇彩、5 美元眼线笔将支持全球（暂时不包括土耳其、中国）用户购买。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">Free People 发布<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/free-people-july-catalog-2016-edita-vilkeviciute/\" rel=\"nofollow\">七月潮流特辑</a>：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713082923MpdDjeCH1iEkRN0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669994\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713082923OU83vb0jiuRKoIPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669994\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713082924xiZyv76eSfIcQ9hV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670113\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607130829250eMo7RLErIXpnF1N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669994\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713082926SnaLVc2li3WbPI1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669994\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713082928mILio7Ppw1yvTDCW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669994\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\">Coach 发布<a href=\"http://www.buro247.me/fashion/news/a-new-york-moment-coach-s-fall-winter-16-campaign.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 2016 秋冬广告特辑</a>：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713102551ZIdPCHaAX6ziG1DJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.820313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713102552csJvbufS9YmjIQnB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713102552jH9DxcZf8XGI3YT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\